    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "The visages of beasts are carved into the painted wood of a *beast staff*, with a large head on top. The staff is a *+1 striking staff*. While wielding the staff while you have it prepared, you\u2019re affected by *speak with animals*. If you have Animal Empathy, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus on checks using it.",
